billEvents.eventText: REFERRED TO HOUSING, CONSTRUCTION AND COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT

title: Expands the New York state low income housing tax credit program to certain one to four family residences
summary: Expands the New York state low income housing tax credit program to certain one to four family residences, including a cooperative or a condominium unit.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the public housing law, in relation to expanding the New York state low income housing tax credit program to certain one to four family residences
